contentrichtext.text: {{wiktionarypar|trunk}} '''Trunk''' may refer to: In '''biology''': *[[Elephant#Trunk|Trunk]], the proboscis of an elephant ( elephants trunk) *Synonym for [[torso]] *[[Trunk (botany)]], a tree's central superstructure *[[Nerve trunk]] '''Containers''': *[[Trunk (automobile)]], a large storage compartment *[[Trunk (luggage)]] *[[Trunk (motorcycle)]], a storage compartment '''Other uses''': *[[Trunk (software)]], in revision control *[[Trunk (structural)]], a chute or conduit, or a watertight shaft connecting two or more decks. *[[Trunk line]], in telecommunications *[[Trunk shot]], auto-trunk camera work *[[Trunk Records]], a record label <!-- This has been a rd lk for 11 months per [http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Trunk&diff=116978467&oldid=115106155]; see also [[Talk:Byford Dolphin#Trunk]]:--> *[[Trunk road]] ==See also== *"[[Buttocks#Synonyms|Junk in the trunk]]", or buttocks *"[[Junk in the Trunk]]", an episode of the television series ''Robot Chicken'' *[[Trunking]], network design strategy *[[Trunking (auto)]], riding in trunk or boot *[[Trunks (disambiguation)]] *[[Elephant's trunk (disambiguation)]] {{disambig}} [[cs:Chobot]] [[hu:Chobot]]
